meaning_str.bing:
n. 表；桌子；一览表；台子
v. （正式）提出；（将主意、建议等）搁置
网络. 表格；数据表；餐桌

（正式）提出；（将主意、建议等）搁置

桌子；餐桌；台子；工作台；表；列表；表格；排名榜；积分表；乘法表；平面；议案；议题；饭菜；供应的食物；（会议或谈判的）谈判桌；（就餐或玩牌等的）一桌人
搁置；（正式）提出；提交（议案等）以供讨论；把…列入议事日程

1.en: Therefore, the choice of the project mainly walking, running, climbing, badminton, table tennis is simple, easy to implement project-based.
1.cn: 因此在项目的选择上主要以散步、跑步、登山、羽毛球、乒乓球等简单易行，易于实施的项目为主。

2.en: A range of deals of all sizes are on the table, making the company prone to a reshaping, the people familiar with the matter said.
2.cn: 知情人士说，他们提出了大大小小的各种交易，使该公司可能进行重组。

3.en: We may begin with one, and that "a little one, " and yet it will "become a thousand. " The LORD is great at the multiplication table.
3.cn: 我们开始可能只是「一」，而且是小小的「一」，但它可变成千，这是上帝奇妙的乘法表。

0.en: This is history, right here at this table.
0.cn: 这就是历史，发生在这张桌子上的事。

1.en: Hold on. Sheldon, is there ketchup on that table?
1.cn: 等下，谢尔顿，那边桌子上的是番茄酱吗？

2.en: Ready or not, here I come! Oh, George isn't hiding under the table! But George always hides under the table!
2.cn: 藏好了吗，我来找你咯。噢，乔治这次没有藏在桌子底下。但是乔治每次都藏在桌子底下的。

3.en: And you leave the Book on the table with the flowers.
3.cn: 再把书放在有花的桌子上。

4.en: Our table will be ready in a couple minutes. Yeah. So…
4.cn: 我们的桌子马上就会准备好。

5.en: Look on the table in front of you. Open the envelope.
5.cn: 看看你们面前的桌子，打开那个信封。

6.en: You're table's ready sir. Oh. Good to see you guys. Yes.
6.cn: 您的桌子准备好了。很高兴遇见你们。好。

7.en: So they said our table will be ready in just a few minutes. Oh great. Yeah.
7.cn: 我们的桌子马上就准备好。太棒了。

8.en: A little tight, isn't it? Why didn't you get a bigger table?
8.cn: 有点挤，不是吗？ 你为什么不订大一点的桌子呢？

9.en: Okay, so it's just because it was my table, I have to buy a new one?
9.cn: 那么就因为这是我的桌子，就得让我买新的？

10.en: No. Here's your mail. Thanks. You can just put it on the table.
10.cn: 不，这是你的信。谢谢，你把它放在桌子上就行了。

11.en: Now spread them out on the table face down. Pick one, look at it. Okay.
11.cn: 正面朝下，摊在桌子上，挑一张，看一眼。好的。

12.en: I don't think putting him down the far end of the table's put him in a very chatty mood.
12.cn: 他被安排在了桌子边上，好像不太想聊天呢。

13.en: This is the table I sat at with my parents. This is the chair I sat in.
13.cn: 我和我父母当年就坐在这张桌子边，我就坐在这张椅子上。

14.en: Let me tell you what I think might be going on. No-no-no, don't look at the table. Look at me.
14.cn: 我来告诉你我的想法，不要看桌子，看着我。

15.en: Monica look. Look. Here is that table that I ordered. You got it from Pottery Barn?
15.cn: 莫妮卡，你看这里有我订的桌子。你是在陶瓷货仓买的？

16.en: No. Joey. Come on Rach. No one saw me take it. There was a whole table full of them.
16.cn: 不，乔伊。没有人看到我把它拿走，整个桌子上都是奖杯。

17.en: All right, let's just say for argument's sake that this table here represents the next year and a half, all right?
17.cn: 单纯地打个比方，这张桌子就是未来一年半。

18.en: Ok, that's enough stirring. You two sit at the table while I cook the pancakes.
18.cn: 好了，搅拌的已经很充分了。你们两个坐在桌子旁边，我来做煎饼。

19.en: That's the rule. What rule? There's no rule. If anything, you owe me a table.
19.cn: 规则上讲是的。什么规则？没有什么规则，如果有，就是你欠我个桌子。
